299
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:26,163
Good for you.

300
00:16:26,231 --> 00:16:28,666
Can we go home now?

301
00:16:43,315 --> 00:16:45,116
Welcome, museum members,

302
00:16:45,183 --> 00:16:48,719
