your ancestors.

308
00:17:07,506 --> 00:17:09,173
What?!
I thought you knew.

309
00:17:09,241 --> 00:17:10,841
You all evolved

310
00:17:10,909 --> 00:17:13,811
from some filth-gobbling
nanobots I designed.

311
00:17:13,879 --> 00:17:16,948
