your ponds a few days ago.

312
00:17:17,015 --> 00:17:19,884
But, but this is
creationist talk.

313
00:17:19,952 --> 00:17:21,352
He speaks lies.

314
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:24,188
The Earth was created
in eons, not days.

315
00:17:24,256 --> 00:17:27,892
Yes, relative to you,
it was eons, but, well,

316
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:30,928
