crimes against science.

321
00:17:45,010 --> 00:17:47,278
No...!

322
00:17:47,346 --> 00:17:49,714
Could you drag me
by the restroom?

323
00:17:57,222 --> 00:17:59,623
Go back to Roboklahoma!

324
00:17:59,691 --> 00:18:01,192
Order!

325
00:18:01,259 --> 00:18:03,828
<i>In the matter
of Everyone v. Farnsworth,</i>

326
00:18:03,895 --> 00:18:07,198
the alleged creationist faces
a sentence of death by melting.

327
00:18:07,265 --> 00:18:09,867
